                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-97-off560 t18320906-97-cd561"></join>, 2 bottles, value 4d.; 1 pint of wine, value 2s., and 1 pint of gin, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-97-victim882" type="victimName">
